.Dd September 16, 2006
.Dt VARNISHSTAT 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm varnishstat
.Nd HTTP accelerator statistics
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl 1
.Op Fl V
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility displays statistics from a running
.Xr varnishd 1
instance.
.Pp
The following options are available:
.Bl -tag -width Fl
.It Fl 1
Instead of presenting of a continuously updated display, print the
statistics once and exit.
.It Fl V
Display the version number and exit.
.El
.Pp
The columns in the main display are, from left to right:
.Bl -enum
.It
Total since startup
.It
Delta since last update (normally the last second)
.It
Average over process lifetime
.It
Descriptive text
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr varnishd 1 ,
.Xr varnishhist 1 ,
.Xr varnishlog 1 ,
.Xr varnishncsa 1 ,
.Xr varnishtop 1 ,
.Xr curses 3
